&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;相比菜刀，主厨刀更加纤细轻巧，切熟食、水果等非常方便。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMVYMb9W7WvdHiaRIdkxbtibcvnCUH8y4jHA0xocV8Wh1O5hjomhITArsg/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;550&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7509090909090909&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMVYMb9W7WvdHiaRIdkxbtibcvnCUH8y4jHA0xocV8Wh1O5hjomhITArsg/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;刀刃同样锋利，切寿司，手起刀落就切好了，一点也不拖泥带水。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMtSpwibaDlDMKoicHkakUmAl90LFdQzcfdYIEvIReicAhHPicAK0dOwqcYw/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;430&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7511627906976744&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMtSpwibaDlDMKoicHkakUmAl90LFdQzcfdYIEvIReicAhHPicAK0dOwqcYw/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;418&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;切硬硬的腊肠，依旧轻松。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMRic5OUbkw5FGTxzU0TjBruiaicfZKA77tFgsdOtldibTVz7HicgPczZpSGQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;470&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7510638297872341&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMRic5OUbkw5FGTxzU0TjBruiaicfZKA77tFgsdOtldibTVz7HicgPczZpSGQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;418&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;切柠檬、苹果、番茄等，更是没问题。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; 使用&amp;amp;保养建议&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMU9ZthNicfibriafviaQve2YpseyhLXd7GknT2JKwz7Yj38iaYCTQGa1l2Uw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SMU9ZthNicfibriafviaQve2YpseyhLXd7GknT2JKwz7Yj38iaYCTQGa1l2Uw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;磨刀器，有粗磨、细磨两个模式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;粗磨：用于开刃、修复受损严重的刀刃，每次3~5下。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;细磨：用于消除刀口上的毛刺，将刀刃打磨平滑光亮，每次&lt;span&gt;3~5下&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;使用时，一只手握紧磨刀器，并固定在平面上。另一只手握住刀柄，把刀刃微微倾斜放入磨刀器夹口，朝自己的方向快速拉动即可。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;注：不可以来回拉动刀具，否则容易损伤刀刃。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SM0Ff5hu3oxhLYu96Mefe6ibRffsJ59NzePPmxKJ4od76rRHJCczwLAkw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ6icXrBQibiceIvkBMic4hcI1SM0Ff5hu3oxhLYu96Mefe6ibRffsJ59NzePPmxKJ4od76rRHJCczwLAkw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;因为黑刀的表面有一层氧化膜，光滑致密、不易沾污，非常好清洗。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;用清水冲洗干净后，自然晾干就好。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

